{"tid":457911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【炒狗話無風險】網售iPhone X中伏 賣家遇男女賊當街被搶3機","createTime":"2017-11-04T10:43:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T10:47:10.000Z","uid":294,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"24e116e77c00382cb7764b2bc8c7eadfe9916d3e","tid":457911,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T10:43:14.000Z","msg":"九龍塘發生搶iPhone X事件！一名男子於網上放售3部iPhone X，相約買家今日到港鐵九龍塘站外交收。至今日下午5時許，事主與買家見面後，對方聲稱已用銀行過數，惟事主收不到款項，雙方發生爭執，其間事主遭對方揮拳打傷面，並遭搶去3部iPhone X，男女賊人得手後登上接應的私家車逃去。事主頭部受傷流血，地上遺下血迹，他事後由救護車送往醫院治理，警員則封鎖現場調查，並在附近一帶兜截賊人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/184155_0b4af1057ec4a2165239d4d0d85547b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F184155_0b4af1057ec4a2165239d4d0d85547b2.jpg&h=dcaddce6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76454dd4cbbe8e74d188e944e0c3f4957ab284d","tid":457911,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T10:44:26.000Z","msg":"人地真係出盡奶力搵9千啦<br />\n班炒狗先搵幾舊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d8af0323d283e5e1968b5abf06e11d72c2cb80","tid":457911,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T10:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171103/large/1509705181_b2ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171103%2Flarge%2F1509705181_b2ee.jpg&h=f4735620&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067317b82afc713b95a8aeebea89b721